quest Generator](/tools/connection-request-generator)\n\n### InMail Generator\nCraft compelling InMail messages to recruiters and hiring managers.\n→ [InMail Generator](/tools/inmail-generator)\n\n### Follow-Up Message Generator\nNever miss a follow-up with professionally crafted messages.\n→ [Follow-Up Message Generator](/tools/follow-up-message)\n\n## Interview Prep: Free Tool\n\n### Interview Questions Generator\nGenerate practice questions tailored to any role or company type.\n→ [Interview Questions Generator](/tools/interview-questions-generator)\n\n## Content & Brand Building: Free Tools\n\n### Post Generator\nCreate engaging LinkedIn posts with tone selector (Professional, Casual, Bold).\n→ [Post Generator](/tools/post-generator)\n\n### Banner Maker\nCreate a professional LinkedIn banner that downloads as a real PNG file.\n→ [Banner Maker](/tools/banner-maker)\n\n## How Much This Saves You\n\n| Service | Typical Cost | LinkForge |\n|---------|-------------|----------|\n| Profile review | $200-$500 | Free |\n| Resume writing | $300-$800 | Free |\n| Cover letter writing | $100-$300 | Free |\n| LinkedIn coaching | $150-$500/hr | Free |\n| Total saved | $750-$2,100+ | $0 |\n\n## Get Started\n\nAll 45+ tools are permanently free. No account required. No credit card. No trial period.\n\n[Explore all free tools →](/tools)',
